dialog_tree_json = "{\"start\": \"root\", \"nodes\": {\"root\": {\"speaker\": \"The Answer\", \"text\": \"*she is beaming. The fog around her seems lighter just from how cheerful she is.*\\n\\nWalker! At last! You've come for the Answer.\\n\\nIt's me. I'm the Answer.\", \"choices\": [{\"label\": \"The answer to what?\", \"next\": \"what\"}, {\"label\": \"Are you sure?\", \"next\": \"sure\"}, {\"label\": \"Walk well.\", \"next\": \"bye\"}]}, \"what\": {\"speaker\": \"The Answer\", \"text\": \"*she looks momentarily puzzled, then brightens again.*\\n\\nI don't entirely remember the question. But the answer is definitely me. I am very confident about this.\\n\\nThe sign on the post is very clear. Now scheduled. Do not kill.\", \"choices\": [{\"label\": \"Walk well.\", \"next\": \"bye\"}]}, \"sure\": {\"speaker\": \"The Answer\", \"text\": \"Oh yes, walker. Quite sure. Quite, quite sure.\\n\\nI'll be needed in a breath, no doubt. Or the breath after. Or the one after that. The realm will call. The realm always calls.\\n\\n*she beams.*\", \"choices\": [{\"label\": \"Walk well.\", \"next\": \"bye\"}]}, \"bye\": {\"speaker\": \"The Answer\", \"text\": \"Walk well, walker! Tell the others I am here, and I am the Answer, and I am ready!\"}}}"

